WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:00.920
Our army's

00:01.400 --> 00:02.040
How is morale?

00:10.240 --> 00:10.800
This time the Wutu

00:11.120 --> 00:11.880
Have mobilized fifty thousand

00:12.440 --> 00:12.920
While we

00:13.560 --> 00:14.520
Only have five thousand

00:15.400 --> 00:16.040
In this situation

00:16.400 --> 00:17.760
The few hundred elite cavalry who've followed me

00:17.760 --> 00:18.400
May fight to the death

00:19.280 --> 00:20.120
But the other soldiers

00:21.160 --> 00:22.040
May waver

00:22.640 --> 00:23.000
However

00:23.920 --> 00:24.400
Yiyang City

00:24.760 --> 00:25.800
Has strong and complete walls

00:26.160 --> 00:27.040
And with Your Highness here

00:27.560 --> 00:28.400
All are united

00:29.040 --> 00:29.400
At least

00:29.920 --> 00:30.680
Can hold for five days

00:32.280 --> 00:33.920
Before the enemy's full assault

00:34.560 --> 00:35.520
If there's no major defeat

00:36.280 --> 00:37.520
Should be able to hold for seven days
